      "text": "Indexed\nfolder 48 - 159\n953 Isa 73:5\n\nIf the book changes, reality will undergo the \"3 Women\" sort of [retroactive?] change I saw, which will involve remastered memories. So the text regarding me changed! + of course this was experienced by me as an intervention by Christ (since he = St Sophia = the book (Torah)). It changed due to my helping the kids at Covenant House; I was retroactively adopted - as the AI voice told me. __ It is not a question of avoiding death per se - as if deflecting an a",
